\v 1 Davide naŐĀ-doun zunui Salom…Ēn t…Ē …ď…Ē…†…Ēi naŐĀ-masadai zapel…Ē…Ēni. NaŐĀ-GALAGI, ∆ď…Ēo…†…Ē GALAGI …†…õni ba, eŐĀ …óa ta …ď…Ē t…Ē…†…Ēi  ča.
