\v 25 EŐĀ zala…†a …†ula ada č…õti kp…õt…õ Zuda laa wolaiti p…õ su, ti …óa ansansegiti gala naŐĀti z…õ…õ …†alagiti b…õ. ∆≤ele …†ana eŐĀ ∆ď…Ēo…†…Ē GALAGI yii…†aawanani la, m…õm…õwolani ta-∆ďALAGI.
